oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: fund raising
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and orange on white) announcing St. Jude Jam 2016 to benefit St. Jude's Children's Research Hospital. Event features Big Rich, Kelsea Ballerini, Chase Rice, Maddie and Tae, Easton Corbin, Eric Paslay, and Cam at the Grizzly Rose bar on October 18. Poster is a limited edition of 100.
